ActCanada National Parks Act
SubjectRegulations Amending Certain Regulations Made Under the Canada National Park Act (Miscellaneous Program)
PrecisRegulations Amending CERTAIN REGULATIONS MADE UNDER THE CANADA NATIONAL PARKS ACT (MISCELLANEOUS PROGRAM) in order to (1) align the French and English versions; (2) update obsolete references; (3) add clarity to regulatory provisions; (4) correct regulatory authorities; and, (5) modify the name of a National Historic Site.
